---
title: Double BBQ-Spiced Chicken Drumsticks with Roast Potatoes, Pear Slaw & Beetroot Relish
description: Get ready to drum up some excitement with our spiced chicken drumsticks and roast potatoes. Add a pop of colour and extra flavour with a crunchy pear slaw and a dollop of beetroot relish – it’s a party on your plate!
